                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">Australian Federal Law</h2>
                        <p class="text-slate-500">Fair Work Act 2009 & Associated Acts</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">Federal laws prohibit an employer from taking 'adverse action' (like dismissal or demotion) against an employee or job applicant based on the following protected attributes:</p>
                <div class="space-y-3">
                    <details class="bg-slate-50 rounded group">
                        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-3 cursor-pointer">
                            <span class="font-semibold">Personal & Physical Attributes</span>
                            <span class="arrow-down transition-transform duration-300">▼</span>
                        </summary>
                        <ul class="p-3 border-t border-slate-200 list-disc list-inside text-slate-600 space-y-1">
                            <li>Race or colour</li>
                            <li>Sex, sexual orientation, gender identity, or intersex status</li>
                            <li>Age</li>
                            <li>Physical or mental disability</li>
                        </ul>
                    </details>
                    <details class="bg-slate-50 rounded group">
                        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-3 cursor-pointer">
                            <span class="font-semibold">Family & Relationship Status</span>
                            <span class="arrow-down transition-transform duration-300">▼</span>
                        </summary>
                        <ul class="p-3 border-t border-slate-200 list-disc list-inside text-slate-600 space-y-1">
                            <li>Marital status</li>
                            <li>Family or carer's responsibilities</li>
                            <li>Pregnancy or breastfeeding</li>
                            <li>Experiencing family and domestic violence</li>
                        </ul>
                    </details>
                    <details class="bg-slate-50 rounded group">
                        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-3 cursor-pointer">
                            <span class="font-semibold">Beliefs & Background</span>
                            <span class="arrow-down transition-transform duration-300">▼</span>
                        </summary>
                        <ul class="p-3 border-t border-slate-200 list-disc list-inside text-slate-600 space-y-1">
                            <li>Religion</li>
                            <li>Political opinion</li>
                            <li>National extraction (place of birth or ancestry)</li>
                            <li>Social origin (class or caste)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </details>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- NSW State Law Column -->
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                     <div class="bg-green-100 text-green-700 rounded-full h-12 w-12 flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
