                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">New South Wales Law</h2>
                        <p class="text-slate-500">Anti-Discrimination Act 1977</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">The NSW Act provides specific protections against discrimination in employment. While there is significant overlap with Federal law, the grounds are defined as follows:</p>
                <div class="space-y-3">
                     <details class="bg-slate-50 rounded group">
                        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-3 cursor-pointer">
                            <span class="font-semibold">Personal & Physical Attributes</span>
                            <span class="arrow-down transition-transform duration-300">▼</span>
                        </summary>
                        <ul class="p-3 border-t border-slate-200 list-disc list-inside text-slate-600 space-y-1">
                            <li>Race (includes colour, nationality, descent)</li>
                            <li>Sex (includes pregnancy and breastfeeding)</li>
                            <li>Age</li>
                            <li>Disability (past, present, or future)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </details>
                     <details class="bg-slate-50 rounded group">
                        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-3 cursor-pointer">
                            <span class="font-semibold">Identity & Relationship Status</span>
                            <span class="arrow-down transition-transform duration-300">▼</span>
                        </summary>
                        <ul class="p-3 border-t border-slate-200 list-disc list-inside text-slate-600 space-y-1">
                            <li>Homosexuality (sexual orientation)</li>
                            <li>Transgender status (gender identity)</li>
                             <li>Marital or domestic status</li>
                            <li>Carer's responsibilities</li>
                        </ul>
                    </details>
                </div>
            </div>

        </main>
        
        <footer class="mt-12 text-center border-t pt-8">
            <p class="text-lg font-semibold">A Dual Layer of Protection</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">Both federal and state laws work together to provide a broad safety net against discrimination. This ensures that employment decisions are based on merit, skills, and qualifications, not on irrelevant personal characteristics.</p>
        </footer>
